title: Week 3 Studs & Duds + Free Willy - Fantasy Football Podcast for 9/27
description:
The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode! On today’s fantasy football podcast, Andy, Mike, and Jason discuss the Studs & Duds of Week 3! Get a recap of the week winning performances, the players to be most concerned about going forward, and a number of big injuries. Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for September 27th, 2021.
  
 Support the Tagliere Family: https://www.gofundme.com/f/support-the-tagliere-family
  
 (02:50) - Monday Punday
 (05:25) - NFL News
 (17:20) - Week 3 Studmuffins 
 (17:25) - QB Studs
 (25:00) - RB Studs 
 (37:25) - WR Studs
 (48:05) - TE Studs
 (49:30) - Week 3 Duds
 (49:40) - QB Duds
 (54:30) - RB Duds
 (57:30) - WR Duds
 (01:02:30) - TE Duds
